    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and place in the <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until toasted and crispy</p><p>Once toasted, spread a generous knob of <strong>butter</strong> over the <strong>toasted ciabatta</strong> – this is your <strong>crispy buttered ciabatta</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
