    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Irish-style coddle sausage & potato stew</strong> with the <strong>crispy buttered ciabatta </strong>to the side and discard the <strong>bay leaf[ves]</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped parsley</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
